data.description: WOW!!! Are you ready for an amazing opportunity to own a larger corner lot that is a little over an acre mol and close to all Neosho has to offer? This property INCLUDES a large storage building, a covered front porch, you can sit on the front porch and enjoy the breeze along with beautiful scenery while the kids play in the yard, the inside of the house offers a large living room with dining area, 3 bedrooms, utility room for your washer and dryer just off the kitchen and more. Being sold "As IS".
